<h3 id="automatic-page-numbers">Automatic Page Numbers</h3>

<p>Add page numbers on A-Grid-Folios using <span class="command">Shift-âŒ¥-âŒ˜-N</span>. Give the numbers their own paragraph style named Folios. Itâ€™s a good idea to set the alignment of the page folios to Away from Spine or Center.</p>

<h4 id="grep-style">GREP Style</h4>

<p>In your body copy paragraph style, go to GREP Styles. Make it that each instance of the words <span style="color: red;">Supreme Court</span> is coloured red.</p>

